  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If tomorrow were doomsday, would you save the world or spend your last moments with a loved one?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292340/extras/ebc5aa67f0f2ee475c40868658806e7c.avif?t=1748424381\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Childhood Sweetheart :</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"I’ll stay with you, now and forever.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292340/extras/68ccc2a1f331fab52cd6c3552ad8608e.avif?t=1748424381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292340/extras_big/68ccc2a1f331fab52cd6c3552ad8608e.avif?t=1748424381 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Bold and Decisive Sexy Spy:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Faith, mission, emotions? They’re illusions. Only control ensures survival.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292340/extras/01a39a411b1a460024b0aaea05826228.avif?t=1748424381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292340/extras_big/01a39a411b1a460024b0aaea05826228.avif?t=1748424381 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mysterious genius girl:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"You’re the only light in my life and the connection to this world.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292340/extras/97cd7c6d6b9d2822cc0a4b38c3b48c71.avif?t=1748424381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292340/extras_big/97cd7c6d6b9d2822cc0a4b38c3b48c71.avif?t=1748424381 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gentle Intellectual Maid:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Cry if you need to. I’m here.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292340/extras/a82ed41dd13dae6d377b27a6f2935639.avif?t=1748424381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292340/extras_big/a82ed41dd13dae6d377b27a6f2935639.avif?t=1748424381 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Innocent noble girl:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Take me with you. Let’s run away together!\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292340/extras/56460bae7beb4dcb163c25bfd5c8c43b.avif?t=1748424381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292340/extras_big/56460bae7beb4dcb163c25bfd5c8c43b.avif?t=1748424381 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > If you’re into dangerous and beautiful bad girls, we’ve got that too...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Let's just stay in this moment, and after tonight, forget me.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Endless Exploration:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hundreds endings. Every choice shapes the story, making each player’s journey unique with hidden content to discover.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>New Adventure:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fictional world offers endless possibilities. Experience epic romance and thrilling adventure, crafting your own epic tale.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Diverse Gameplay:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rich interactive content—exploration, combat, and collection—delivers ultimate satisfaction and immersion. The adventure never ends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Ultimate Visuals:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Five distinct heroines—cool, elegant, charming, romantic, and seductive—accompany you across different eras and cultures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
